cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.RO, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with Deep Reinforcement Learning (DRL) and its vulnerability to adversarial perturbations on state observations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also utilizes tools from the neural network verification literature, which suggests a possible fit with cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
